  "detailed_description": "Voxelgram is a 3D nonograms game where solving puzzles feels like sculpting in three dimensions. Reveal voxel models as you complete each challenge.<br><br>Features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>256 Puzzles: Tackle 256 unique puzzles, organized into 26 beautifully crafted dioramas.<br></li><li>User-Generated Content: Discover over 1,400 puzzles from the community through Workshop support.<br></li><li>Procedural Generation: Enjoy endless replayability with procedurally generated puzzles.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1158470/extras/3dd710c133203e34c5dba4a26b143c4f.avif?t=1770799042\" width=550 height=417 /></span>",
